### testes da integração mock pagar.me

### 1. ver status da integração
GET http://localhost:7000/api/paymentmock/integration-status
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. pega cenários de teste disponíveis
GET http://localhost:7000/api/paymentmock/test-scenarios
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. simular pagamento aprovado
POST http://localhost:7000/api/paymentmock/simulate-pagarme
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100.00,
  "customerName": "João Silva",
  "customerEmail": "joao.silva@test.com",
  "cardNumber": "4111111111111111",
  "cardHolderName": "João Silva",
  "expirationDate": "1225",
  "cvv": "123"
}

